lines.text: On 25 Sep 2025, we examined the above patient.
Our examination yielded the following findings:
The cervical lymph nodes were assessed and appear unremarkable in size, shape. vascularity and
overall appearance. They do not possess any significant features demonstrable with ultrasound
The bilateral submandibular glands were assessed and appear unremarkable.
The bilateral parotid glands were assessed and appear unremarkable.
Bilateral, mildly enlarged submandibular lymph nodes measured:
A 0.5 x 0.4 x 0.4 cm cyst is seen at the right submandibular gland.
Bilateral, mildly enlarged submandibular lymph nodes of normal morphology.
"ANY CLINICAL OR PATHOLOGICAL FOLLOW-UP PERTINENT TO THIS EXAMINATION WOULD BE APPRECIATED
